      "content": "Pseudoephedrine is not generally recommended for pregnant women, especially early on, because it can cause some side effects. Since you need relief now, I suggest you try a very small dose, but only if you absolutely must, and keep a close eye on how you feel. For immediate relief, try steaming your sinuses with hot, moist towels, and maybe a warm bath.",
