      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks, that makes me feel a bit better. how much do you think i should take? like, would 60mg be okay just to get some sleep? i really don't want to drive to an emergency room for a stuffy nose, so i'd rather just take this and deal with the doctor in the morning.",
